			Article        
		
| Journal of Asian Studies
		
		
		
		
		
		
		

China, Unincorporated: Company Law and Business Enterprise in Twentieth Century China
William C. Kirby
Keywords: Business Ventures; 
				  Law; 
				  China; 
				  

